                            <comment id="12737813" author="ehatcher" created="Sat, 1 Aug 2009 03:06:13 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;simple patch to simply set $hasMore to false once it is processed.  The scenario mentioned in the e-mail thread is alleviated with this patch.  That&apos;s the extent of my testing.  Anyone see anything wrong?  If not, I&apos;ll commit in a few days.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12737829" author="noble.paul" created="Sat, 1 Aug 2009 05:04:12 +0100"  >&lt;p&gt;it should be removed , instead of setting to false. $nextUrl also can be removed along with it&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
